                    "line_text": "De corbeaux hagards, fait gémir l'éther.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Il est, Vérité, ton ministre amer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
